Durban - Premier Hotel Edwardian is located 1km from the Port Edward city centre and conveniently close to spectacular beaches, world-class golf courses and local tourist attractions. The hotel offers panoramic views of the Indian Ocean and lush coastal hillsides. Premier Hotel Edwardian boasts 39 Tuscan-styled rooms and suites that are beautifully decorated and provide the utmost comfort, while offering excellent conference facilities for product launches or corporate events, ensuring that the hotel is suited for business and leisure travellers alike. The hotel restaurant offers guests a place to unwind, relax, and enjoy exceptional food and good wine. Experience the South Coast from the comfort of Premier Hotel Edwardian. Independent Traveller * Contact the reservations on 039 311 3618 or see www.premierhotels.co.za to make your next reservation.